<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Brain Exercise - Dementia Care</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons+Outlined" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #e0f7fa;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }
        .exercise-card {
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            width: 280px;
            height: 350px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            text-align: center;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .exercise-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .exercise-card .card-header {
            background-color: #66bb6a;
            color: white;
            font-size: 18px;
            padding: 10px;
        }
        .exercise-card .card-body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
        }
        .exercise-card .card-body p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #555;
        }
        .exercise-card .btn {
            background-color: #66bb6a;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .exercise-card .btn:hover {
            background-color: #388e3c;
        }
        .container {
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        .card-deck {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            color: #66bb6a;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .instructions {
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .section-title {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #388e3c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <!-- Include Navbar -->
    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <!-- Section Title -->
        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Services</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Brain Exercise Cards -->
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Brain Exercise for Dementia Care</h2>

        <div class="card-deck">
            <!-- Memory Card Game -->
            <div class="exercise-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Memory Card Matching</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-outlined">memory</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Enhance memory and cognitive skills through a fun memory card matching game.</p>
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <p>Match pairs of cards and improve memory retention. Take your time!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="/games/memory-card-matching" class="btn">Start Game</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Word Search -->
            <div class="exercise-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Word Search</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-outlined">search</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Test your vocabulary and cognitive function with a relaxing word search game.</p>
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <p>Find hidden words from the list. Relax and enjoy the challenge.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="/games/word-search" class="btn">Start Word Search</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Brain Teasers -->
            <div class="exercise-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Brain Teasers</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-outlined">lightbulb</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Engage in fun brain teasers that challenge your reasoning and logic skills.</p>
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <p>Think outside the box and challenge yourself with interesting brain teasers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="/games/brain-teasers" class="btn">Try Brain Teasers</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Simon Says Game -->
            <div class="exercise-card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h5 class="mb-0">Simon Says</h5>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <span class="material-icons-outlined">gamepad</span>
                    </div>
                    <p>Follow the pattern of colors and shapes in Simon Says for a memory challenge.</p>
                    <div class="instructions">
                        <p>Pay attention to the sequence and repeat the pattern correctly to win!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <a href="/games/simon-says" class="btn">Play Simon Says</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Set Up Your Day Section -->
        <div class="section-title">
            <h3>Set Up Your Day</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-center">Organize your day by adding tasks and activities to your to-do list.</p>
        <div class="text-center">
            <a href="/todo" class="btn btn-success">Open To-Do List</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Include Footer -->
    <%- include('footer') %>

</body>
</html>
